Class QSetTransln

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.translations.QSetTransln
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AppConstants, QuestionConstants, TranslnConstants, XMLConstants

    public class QSetTransln
extends Object
implements QuestionConstants, TranslnConstants
    Holds the translation of all of the questions in a master-authored question set into a single language.
